# 🎬 Movie Recommendation System
A Flask-based Movie Recommendation System developed as the Major Project for the **iNeuBytes AI/ML Internship**.
The application recommends similar movies based on the movie selected by the user using **Content-Based Filtering**, **TF-IDF Vectorization**, and **Cosine Similarity**.
---
## Features
- Content-Based Movie Recommendation
- Simple and User-Friendly Interface
- Fast Recommendation Generation
- Error Handling for Invalid Movie Names
- REST API using Flask
- Deployed on Render
---
## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Joblib
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
---
## Dataset
Dataset: MovieLens Movies Dataset
Source:
https://grouplens.org/datasets/movielens/
Dataset File:
```
dataset/movies.csv
```
